                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Although the process was mostly deterministic, completing these repetitive steps manually was not an effective use of time.\n\nThat effort could be better spent on higher-value project work, while manual handoffs also increased the risk of delays, duplicate records, missing information, and inconsistent project setup.",
